description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;St Ann&#39;s Hospice&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At St Ann’s, there’s one thing that motivates us, and that’s providing excellent care and support to those living with or affected by life-limiting illnesses. We’re continuously developing our plans for delivering world-class, innovative care to ensure St Ann’s is in the best shape possible for future generations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be challenged, inspired and empowered to help us achieve our purpose and to play your part in making a difference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Have you got what it takes?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you an inspiring senior leader?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can you demonstrate effective leadership projects and service improvements?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do you have up-to-date and relevant professional knowledge?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You must be passionate about our patients and a collaborative colleague&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Most importantly, you must be wholeheartedly committed to and motivated by the purpose and values of St Ann’s Hospice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting time to join an ambitious, much loved charity and help us achieve our goals. If you’re looking for a new challenge and the opportunity to make a difference, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time permanant position. Hours of ork are 37.5 hours per week 3/5 days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The salary is at St Ann&#39;s pay scale of Band 8a £46,591 per annum.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note this advert will close 27 November 2020 12 Noon. There will be two interview dates, 9 December 2020 and 15 December 2020.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An Enhanced DBS Check will be required, the cost of which is covered by the hospice. St Ann’s Hospice is committed to safeguarding and promoting the welfare of adults at risk and children.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion please call Gill Turnpenney, Director of OD &amp; Support Services on 0161 498 3622&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
